</div>

</div>

<div class="bloc note">

<div class="bloc_ti note_ti">

<span>Reminder</span>

</div>

<div class="txt">

To display the TemporalBox reference icon, select the `Show Box Icons`
option of the `Maquette Preferences` tab.

</div>

</div>

</div>

